FBIS3-38088 "drsov039_a_94038" FBIS-SOV-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Comments on European Security LD2502224594 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 2140 GMT 25 Feb 94 LD2502224594 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] [Announcer] Pavel Grachev, the Russian defense minister, arrived in the Norwegian capital on Friday on a working visit. [passage omitted] [Begin Grachev recording] If we really want to cooperate for peace, if we want two--not two, let us say Russia and NATO to draw together--of course, the priority role should be given to Russia as a great power. It looks like it is pointless to decide issues of security in Europe without Russia. [end recording]
